{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-24","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 24","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Do sada ste naučili kako da kreirate pitanja koristeći glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">to be</span>. U rečenicama sa glagolom <span class=\"highlighted-text\">to be</span> (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">am</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">is</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">are</span>) samo morate promeniti redosled imenice i glagola da biste kreirali pitanje. Kao ovo:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Potvrda</th>\n<th>Pitanje</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">You are a developer.</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Are you a developer?</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Promena redosleda imenica i glagola ne funkcioniše u svakom slučaju. Mnoge rečenice zahtevaju dodavanje pomoćnog glagola za formulisanje pitanja. Jedan od najčešće korišćenih pomoćnih glagola je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">do</span>.</p>\n<p>Možete koristiti glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">do</span> kao pomoćni glagol za mnoge glagole. U prezentu uzima oblik <span class=\"highlighted-text\">do</span> (za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">you</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">we</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">they</span>) i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">does</span> (za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">he</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">she</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">it</span>). To je kao znak koji dodajete na početak vaše rečenice; ovo će svima signalizirati da je ta rečenica pitanje. Na primer:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Potvrda</th>\n<th>Pitanje</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">You debug on Fridays.</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Do you debug on Fridays?</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Poslušaj zvuk i dovrši rečenicu ispod.</p>\n</section>","explanation":null,"challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"English","superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","block":"learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room","lang":"en-US","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-24"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>How about you? BLANK you BLANK any hobbies?</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"Do","feedback":"<p>Ovaj pomoćni glagol se koristi u pitanjima koja pitaju o radnjama, navikama ili činjenicama. Prvo slovo je napisano velikim slovom.</p>"},{"answer":"have","feedback":"<p>To je osnovni oblik glavnog glagola. Ovde pita da li Sofija ima ili obavlja rekreivne aktivnosti.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-breakroom.png","characters":[{"character":"Tom","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"1.3-2.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":8.06,"finishTimestamp":9.72},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":2.66,"dialogue":{"text":"How about you? Do you have any hobbies?","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":3.16,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room","dashedName":"task-24","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers